text: Eulophia taiwanensis is a species of plant in the family Orchidaceae. It is found in Taiwan and the Philippines. == Synonyms == The following are heterotypic synonyms : *Eulophia taiwanensis Hayata, 1911 *Eulophia kitamurae Masam, 1932 *Eulophia segawae Fukuy, 1934 *Eulophia graminea var. kitamurae Masam.)
